OL,8,G0900FAbandoned Engineering
OL,9,     GWe discover a concrete dome, that
OL,10,     Gwas once intended to conceal and
OL,11,     Gprotect Hitler's terrible wonder
OL,12,     Gweapons, and a mysterious
OL,13,     Gbuilding with eerie echoes of the
OL,14,     GCold War.
OL,15,G1000FAbandoned Engineering
OL,16,     GA deserted Spanish town scarred
OL,17,     Gby its brutal wartime past, a
OL,18,     Gghostly fleet of ships, and a
OL,19,     Gbridge to nowhere hidden in a
OL,20,     Gforest are all investigated to
OL,21,     Guncover why they were abandoned.
